What you need to know:

The train with a capacity of up to 1,600 passengers per trip will depart from Nairobi at 8am to arrive in Nanyuki at 2pm. Commuters travelling from Nairobi to Nanyuki were charged Sh200 fare on second class coaches and between Sh50 and Sh100 for inter-terminus trips that will serve Murang’a, Makuyu, Maragua, Sagana, Karatina, Kiganjo, Chaka and Naromoru stations.